{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"89117d59-e7e2-4d74-9470-779bfe82908f","content":"Your `.testsettings` file is a **legacy format** not supported by the modern MSTest runner (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how to migrate each part:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` (30s) | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>` |\n| Assembly resolution | `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>` |\n| Code coverage collector | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n\nLet me create the replacement files:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01Cfr5nwUBjNPZyShGWMG8V6","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01LhCmBrVhAkgoA2YCP8dvoG","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-99f324d5c8c14b1f90c56b49c8d17310/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <!-- Migrated from .testsettings TestTimeout (30 000 ms) -->\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n    <!-- Replaces AssemblyResolution / TestDirectory deployment -->\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\" />\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-99f324d5c8c14b1f90c56b49c8d17310/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01TvFAChe6xR2j6fp8t4M7Nu","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-99f324d5c8c14b1f90c56b49c8d17310/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </Prope